      "updated": 1781273349652,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "## vector database:\n- embedding model -> ubah input jadi vector\n- embedding vector -> hasil dari embedding model\n- chroma ... sentence embedding\n- Sbert\n- google/gemma-3-27b-pt\n    - buatan google\n    - gemma versi 3\n    - 27B parameter\n    - pretrained\n- naming model:\n    - it -> instruction tune. buat conversation\n    - qat -> quantized aware training\n    - q4 -> quantized 4 bit\n- NN -> nearest neighbour algorithm\n- create client, then embedding function\n- document ... terus ada metadata\n    - \n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "## vector database:\n- embedding model -> ubah input jadi vector\n- embedding vector -> hasil dari embedding model\n- chroma ... sentence embedding\n- Sbert\n- google/gemma-3-27b-pt\n    - buatan google\n    - gemma versi 3\n    - 27B parameter\n    - pretrained\n- naming model:\n    - it -> instruction tune. buat conversation\n    - qat -> quantized aware training\n    - q4 -> quantized 4 bit\n- NN -> nearest neighbour algorithm\n- create client, then embedding function\n- document ... terus ada metadata\n    - \n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
